---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="Bits And Bytes IT Solutions | Modern IT Solutions"
	description="Bits And Bytes IT Solutions builds premium websites and software applications for web, mobile, and desktop."
	activePage="home"
>
	<section class="grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[1.25fr_0.75fr] lg:items-center">
		<div class="space-y-7">
			<p class="fade-rise inline-flex rounded-full border border-cyan-200/30 bg-cyan-200/10 px-4 py-1 text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-cyan-100" style="--delay: 80ms;">
				Software Studio for Growth Teams
			</p>
			<h1 class="fade-rise text-4xl font-semibold leading-tight text-white md:text-6xl" style="--delay: 160ms;">
				We engineer websites and applications that turn ideas into durable products.
			</h1>
			<p class="fade-rise max-w-2xl text-lg text-slate-300" style="--delay: 260ms;">
				From high-converting marketing sites to full SaaS platforms, Bits And Bytes IT Solutions combines product strategy, design, and engineering to ship software faster and smarter.
			</p>
			<div class="fade-rise flex flex-wrap gap-3" style="--delay: 340ms;">
				<a href="/services" class="btn-primary">Explore Services</a>
				<a href="/contact" class="btn-secondary">Book a Discovery Call</a>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="glass-card fade-rise space-y-5" style="--delay: 420ms;">
			<p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-cyan-100">Delivery Snapshot</p>
			<ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-slate-200">
				<li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-2 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-cyan-300"></span>Full-cycle web engineering with Angular, TypeScript, and NestJS APIs.</li>
				<li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-2 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-violet-300"></span>Cross-platform app development for mobile and desktop experiences.</li>
				<li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-2 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-cyan-300"></span>Transparent process: roadmap, weekly demos, launch support.</li>
			</ul>
			<div class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-4 text-sm text-slate-300">
				<p class="font-semibold text-white">Need a fast estimate?</p>
				<p>Most MVP projects begin in the $15k-$50k range, depending on scope and integrations.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="mt-14 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-3">
		<article class="glass-card fade-rise" style="--delay: 100ms;">
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Website Development</h2>
			<p class="mt-2 text-slate-300">Conversion-focused websites, landing pages, and content platforms designed to scale with your brand.</p>
		</article>
		<article class="glass-card fade-rise" style="--delay: 180ms;">
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Application Engineering</h2>
			<p class="mt-2 text-slate-300">Robust web, mobile, and desktop software with performance, security, and usability built in from day one.</p>
		</article>
		<article class="glass-card fade-rise" style="--delay: 260ms;">
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Ongoing Product Support</h2>
			<p class="mt-2 text-slate-300">Iterative improvements, analytics-led optimization, and long-term technical guidance after launch.</p>
		</article>
	</section>

	<section class="mt-14">
		<div class="mb-6 flex items-end justify-between gap-4">
			<div>
				<p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-cyan-200">How We Work</p>
				<h2 class="mt-2 text-3xl font-semibold text-white md:text-4xl">A practical process designed for shipping, not stalling.</h2>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-4">
			<article class="glass-card">
				<p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-violet-300">01 Discovery</p>
				<h3 class="mt-2 text-xl font-semibold text-white">Define Goals</h3>
				<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-300">We map requirements, user needs, and key success metrics before any implementation begins.</p>
			</article>
			<article class="glass-card">
				<p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-violet-300">02 Blueprint</p>
				<h3 class="mt-2 text-xl font-semibold text-white">Plan Scope</h3>
				<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-300">You receive a delivery plan with milestones, architecture direction, and clear estimate ranges.</p>
			</article>
			<article class="glass-card">
				<p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-violet-300">03 Build</p>
				<h3 class="mt-2 text-xl font-semibold text-white">Ship Iteratively</h3>
				<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-300">We release in small increments with weekly demos, keeping momentum and reducing project risk.</p>
			</article>
			<article class="glass-card">
				<p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-violet-300">04 Scale</p>
				<h3 class="mt-2 text-xl font-semibold text-white">Optimize Growth</h3>
				<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-300">After launch, we monitor usage, improve performance, and evolve your product roadmap.</p>
			</article>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="mt-14">
		<div class="mb-6 flex flex-wrap items-end justify-between gap-4">
			<div>
				<p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-cyan-200">Example Work</p>
				<h2 class="mt-2 text-3xl font-semibold text-white md:text-4xl">Sample projects and outcomes (placeholders)</h2>
			</div>
			<a href="/contact" class="btn-secondary">Request Full Portfolio</a>
		</div>

		<div class="grid gap-5 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
			<article class="card">
				<div class="h-36 rounded-lg border border-violet-400/30 bg-gradient-to-br from-violet-500/20 to-cyan-500/20"></div>
				<h3 class="mt-4 text-xl font-semibold text-white">SaaS Admin Dashboard</h3>
				<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-300">Placeholder case study: reporting workflows, role-based access, and performance-focused analytics views.</p>
				<p class="mt-3 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-violet-300">Angular + NestJS + MySQL</p>
			</article>

			<article class="card">
				<div class="h-36 rounded-lg border border-cyan-400/30 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-500/20 to-indigo-500/20"></div>
				<h3 class="mt-4 text-xl font-semibold text-white">Service Business Website</h3>
				<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-300">Placeholder case study: redesigned marketing website with stronger messaging and lead-driven page structure.</p>
				<p class="mt-3 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-cyan-300">Astro + Tailwind (Simple Sites)</p>
			</article>

			<article class="card">
				<div class="h-36 rounded-lg border border-violet-400/30 bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-500/20 to-violet-500/20"></div>
				<h3 class="mt-4 text-xl font-semibold text-white">Cross-Platform Field App</h3>
				<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-300">Placeholder case study: operations app concept for teams needing mobile-first task management and offline support.</p>
				<p class="mt-3 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-violet-300">Ionic + Capacitor + Electron</p>
			</article>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="mt-14">
		<div class="mb-6 flex flex-wrap items-end justify-between gap-4">
			<div>
				<p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-cyan-200">Technology Stack</p>
				<h2 class="mt-2 text-3xl font-semibold text-white md:text-4xl">Primary stack for production-grade web, mobile, and desktop products.</h2>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
			<article class="glass-card">
				<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">Frontend</h3>
				<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-300">Angular 20, TypeScript, Angular Material, Ionic UI, SCSS, Tailwind CSS, NgRx, Angular Signals, RxJS.</p>
			</article>
			<article class="glass-card">
				<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">Backend</h3>
				<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-300">Node.js LTS with NestJS (primary), REST APIs, optional GraphQL, JWT/OAuth2 auth flows, RBAC, Swagger.</p>
			</article>
			<article class="glass-card">
				<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">Data & Real-Time</h3>
				<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-300">MySQL 8 with Sequelize, migrations and transactions, plus Socket.IO / NestJS gateways for live features.</p>
			</article>
			<article class="glass-card">
				<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">DevOps</h3>
				<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-300">GitHub Actions CI/CD, Docker + Compose, Nginx reverse proxy, and deployment on VPS or cloud infrastructure.</p>
			</article>
		</div>

		<div class="mt-4 rounded-xl border border-cyan-300/20 bg-cyan-300/5 p-4 text-sm text-slate-200">
			<p><strong class="text-white">Also available:</strong> Astro + Tailwind delivery for simpler websites and lightweight blog-focused builds.</p>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
